{"tid":906303,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"佛州州長計票爭議　民主黨黑人新星直播認輸","createTime":"2018-11-18T00:43:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-19T05:33:51.000Z","uid":130626,"like":5,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":11,"replies":[{"pid":"50ce24096c2b9af91717be53974116e4e2166650","tid":906303,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T00:43:06.000Z","msg":"美國期中選舉在本月6日結束後，佛州州長的選舉結果連日來陷入計票爭議，已超過10天。民主黨政壇新星基爾林（Andrew Gillum）周六（17日）在臉書直播，承認敗選，並恭喜共和黨對手德桑提斯（Ron DeSantis）當選。<br />\n《邁阿密先驅報》報導，39歲的基爾林是塔拉哈西市（Tallahassee）巿長，他原本已在11月6日投票日當天宣布敗選，但因雙方票數差距僅約3.4萬票、即0.41個百分點，因此後來撤回敗選聲明，要求驗票。<br />\n基爾林周六在妻子陪伴下，於直播中說：「我們說過，會戰到最後一票計完的那一刻。現在我們要結束驗票程序，並恭喜德桑提斯先生成為偉大佛州的下一屆州長。」不過他也呼籲佛州的選舉制度能夠更新，「進入21世紀」。　（國際中心／綜合外電報導）<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.appledaily.com.tw/images/ReNews/20181118/640_df6eef8ac49f0148c1ee5d4ff7418165.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.appledaily.com.tw%2Fimages%2FReNews%2F20181118%2F640_df6eef8ac49f0148c1ee5d4ff7418165.jpg&h=2a842ca9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181118/1468511/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181118%2F1468511%2F&d=xfmZOGnpSnlsLVliURnZaTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=a3d7b2fa\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20181118%2F1468511%2F&h=93db7e74\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20181118/1468511/</a>"},{"pid":"e89403be2e1da5dfa8eef5f584a4c88800a638e6","tid":906303,"uid":69213,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T00:50:20.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"b0f2e32721f482f50ab73ec292ef7f80623afbf6","tid":906303,"uid":51701,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-11-18T02:08:48.000Z","msg":"隻nigga甩色<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7aeefd33058a4bc7ff0d60381021d6b38c1f5585"